The paper also mentions social context, which is related to multimedia (MM) and social media (SI), indicating that cs.MM and cs.SI are also possible categories. Finally, the paper discusses the methodology and functionality of various works, which involves natural language processing (NLP) and machine learning (ML), suggesting that cs.CL is a possible category as well.
